02:16.053 --> 02:18.263
I mean, uh, tell him
I'm fine either way.

02:18.263 --> 02:19.272
Can we start?

02:22.768 --> 02:23.769
Should we go in that way?

02:23.769 --> 02:27.773
-Yeah. All right.
