the Ukraine crisis.

02:42.704 --> 02:47.376
We've had this discussion
before on my first visit,
on the terrorists.

02:47.376 --> 02:49.795
I wanted to go over it,
just to be really clear,

02:49.795 --> 02:51.213
because this is
very important to the, uh...

02:51.213 --> 02:54.132
to people who
will be watching this show.

