<i>the suspension of talks</i>
<i>on closer ties could be revived</i>

06:05.156 --> 06:07.033
<i>after the two-day meeting,</i>

06:07.033 --> 06:10.745
<i>but officials said the deal</i>
<i>was off the table for now.</i>

06:45.906 --> 06:49.910
Stone:
<i>From November</i>
<i>to February 20th,</i>

06:49.910 --> 06:53.913
<i>2013 into 14, there was</i>
<i>quite a bit of protest.</i>

06:53.913 --> 06:56.916
<i>I remember him vividly</i>
<i>on television saying it was</i>

06:56.916 --> 06:58.668
a coup in slow motion.

06:58.668 --> 07:03.048
It was pretty evident,
transparent to the Russians.

07:03.048 --> 07:06.426
The Ukraine to us was not--
we were not paying attention.

07:09.387 --> 07:10.722
No... Yeah.

07:11.848 --> 07:12.515
Of course.
Of course.

07:34.079 --> 07:35.747
(translator speaking)

07:40.001 --> 07:41.711
♪ ♪

