<i>Today, the bloodiest day yet.</i>

07:50.095 --> 07:52.430
Newswoman: <i>The protesters</i>
<i>are pushing up towards</i>
<i>the government district,</i>

07:52.430 --> 07:54.641
<i>armed here</i>
<i>with Molotov cocktails,</i>

07:54.641 --> 07:57.727
<i>but we saw handguns</i>
<i>and shotguns too.</i>

07:57.727 --> 08:00.146
Newsman 2:
<i>There is absolutely no doubt</i>
<i>that snipers are working here.</i>

08:00.146 --> 08:03.191
<i>I've counted ten bodies.</i>

08:03.191 --> 08:04.609
♪ ♪

