Newswoman:
<i>There are casualties</i>
<i>on both sides.</i>

08:12.158 --> 08:15.328
(shouting in Ukrainian)

08:15.328 --> 08:18.707
Well, she just said
that there are six
dead people up there.

08:18.707 --> 08:21.084
Not just injured, dead.
