08:26.297 --> 08:28.883
<i>did you get any intelligence</i>
<i>of what was going on?</i>

08:28.883 --> 08:30.051
<i>It's the strangest massacre</i>

08:30.051 --> 08:33.221
<i>because of the number</i>
<i>of casualties of policemen</i>

08:33.221 --> 08:36.808
<i>and the civilians</i>
<i>who were killed indicates--</i>

08:36.808 --> 08:39.144
<i>and the policemen</i>
<i>not firing back,</i>

08:39.144 --> 08:41.813
<i>they were retreating</i>
<i>and called back by Yanukovych.</i>

08:41.813 --> 08:43.648
During that, it seems like
there was this--

08:43.648 --> 08:47.360
a sniper force
that was definitely aiming

08:47.360 --> 08:49.863
at the policemen
and the civilians to create

08:49.863 --> 08:52.323
the chaos necessary
for the takeover.

08:55.285 --> 08:56.453
(sighs)

09:39.913 --> 09:40.371
Well, who were
these snipers?

09:40.371 --> 09:42.749
(Putin speaking)

09:56.471 --> 10:00.725
Have you heard any reports
about the training that was
going on in other cities

10:00.725 --> 10:05.730
of battalion,
of, uh, certain
Right-party Sectors?

10:05.730 --> 10:08.358
Hardened, uh, people
of the right?

10:08.358 --> 10:11.444
Hundred-man units came
to the city, I am told

10:11.444 --> 10:14.781
in the days before
the, uh, the Maidan.

10:14.781 --> 10:16.574
(translator speaking)

11:06.708 --> 11:08.501
It was characterized
in the US press

11:08.501 --> 11:11.880
as if Yanukovych
abandoned Kiev.

11:51.044 --> 11:51.878
(translator speaking)

