Stone:
It was Stalin's old office.

28:50.354 --> 28:52.814
(Putin speaking)

28:52.814 --> 28:54.524
Stone: Yeah.

28:54.524 --> 28:57.194
Translator: Ten years
of Munich speech.

28:57.194 --> 28:58.737
Stone:
He looks good.

28:59.905 --> 29:01.490
Could've been a movie star.

29:04.451 --> 29:05.786
Stone:
February.

29:07.579 --> 29:09.206
So today's the day
you got into trouble.

29:09.873 --> 29:12.209
You had quite an audience.

29:27.307 --> 29:28.892
Stone: Is this
where you work now?

29:28.892 --> 29:30.477
(Putin speaks)

